snippet.title: Apartment News w Amber Ruffin, Jenny Hagel & Jack McBrayer | At-Home Variety Show ft Seth MacFarlane
snippet.description:
Does quarantining in a house beat quarantining in an apartment? We interrupt this broadcast of Amber and Jenny’s “Apartment News” to bring you “House News” with Jack McBrayer! 

Peacock Presents: The At-Home Variety Show Featuring Seth MacFarlane is new weeknights at 7pm/4pm PST.
